race.comment: STARS ARE ALIGNING (10) has filled a minor placing at both runs this time in work and looks close to a maiden win. Peaking now and gets her chance. GERACE (7) finds the maiden win elusive but is knocking on the door. Strips rock-hard fit and is drawn to advantage. Will prove hard to reel in if left alone in front. DRAGON FISH (6) was a big improver her last start when sticking her head out to grab third. Freshened with 40 days and with natural improvement she's a live chance. LOVE SO SWEET (8) returns and looks to have come back in good order, benefiting from a trial win here in readiness. Gets in well with the claim and is expected to make her presence felt. GAME OVER (2) also resumes and comes through the same lead-up trial. Gets 3kgs off with the claim and is worth including.
